(1,'ne', 'menuofakultetu', 'O fakultetu', 'Verzija sa sajta', '<div class="left_box" style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 3px 0px; font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px;"><h2 id="razvoj" style="margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit;">Razvoj fakulteta</h2><br>Društveno opredjeljenje za formiranje visokoškolske nastavno-nauène organizacije u oblasti matematièko-fizièkih nauka zvanièno je konstituisano veæ 1970. godine, kada je Skupština SR Crne Gore donijela Program razvoja visokoškolskih institucija u Crnoj Gori za period 1971-1975. godine. Koncepcija takve institucije tada još nije bila sasvim definisana, tako da se u Programu pominju dva naziva: Institut za matematiku i njene primjene i Matematièko-fizièki fakultet. Veæ u Programu razvoja Univerziteta "Veljko Vlahoviæ" za period 1976-1980. godine pobliže se definiše njena fizionomija, jer se govori o potrebi formiranja Instituta prirodnih nauka, kao zajednièke nastavno-nauène jedinice u okviru Univerziteta.<p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px;"></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; text-align: justify;">Uporedo sa razvojem Tehnièkog fakulteta u Titogradu snažila je kadrovski i njegova katedra za matematiku i fiziku, tako da je transformacijom Tehnièkog fakulteta, koja je dobila društvenu verifikaciju 14. jula 1978. godine, konstituisan Institut za matematiku i fiziku, kao prvi korak u realizaciji Programa razvoja Univerziteta.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; text-align: justify;">Odlukom 7. aprila 1980. godine data je saglasnost na nastavni plan i program Odsjeka za matematiku i Odsjeka za fiziku. Prve generacije studenata na tim odsjecima upisane su školske 1980/81. godine.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; text-align: justify;">Dana 17. maja 1988. godine donijeta je Odluka o davanju saglasnosti o preimenovanju Instituta za matematiku i fiziku u Prirodno-matematièki fakultet (PMF) i transformaciju Odsjeka za matematiku i raèunarske nauke.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; text-align: justify;">Znaèajan korak u razvoju PMF-a predstavlja formiranje Odsjeka za biologiju. Prva generacija studenata na tom odsjeku upisana je školske 1991/92. godine.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; text-align: justify;">Školske 2001/02 godine u okviru Odsjeka za matematiku i raèunarske nauke osnovan je studijski program Raèunarske nauke, a sledeæe godine i primijenjeni studijski program Viša (kasnije Visoka) škola za raèunarstvo i informacione tehnologije.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; text-align: justify;">Od školske 2004/2005. nastava na fakultetu je organizovana po principima jedinstvenog evropskog obrazovnog sistema, u skladu sa Bolonjskom deklaracijom. Školske 2007. godine izvršena je temeljna reorganizacija studijskih programa na PMF-u.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; text-align: justify;">U sastavu PMF-a je, desetak godina, kao posebna organizacija cjelina, radio Univerzitetski raèunarski centar (URC). Zadatak URC je bio servisiranje nastave i nauèno-istraživaèkog rada na Univerzitetu Crne Gore iz oblasti raèunarskih nauka. Sada na PMF-u postoji Raèunarski centar PMF-a kao posebna organizaciona cjelina. Zadatak Raèunarskog centra je servisiranje nastave i nauèno-istraživaèkog rada na Fakultetu iz oblasti raèunarskih nauka i davanje usluga treæim licima.</p><h2 id="studijskiProgrami" style="margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit;">Organizacija nastave</h2>Na fakultetu se nastava organizuje na tri nivoa: osnovne, specijalistièke i magistarske postdiplomske i doktorske studije.&nbsp;<br><br><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px;"><a class="title" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Osnovne studije.</a>&nbsp;U okviru osnovnih studija organizuje se pet akademskih i jedan primijenjeni studijski program:&nbsp;<br>akademski studijski program&nbsp;<a href="http://www.pmf.ucg.ac.me/index.php?page=StudijskiProgramPrikaz&amp;studijski_program=1" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Matematika</a>,<br>akademski studijski program&nbsp;<a href="http://www.pmf.ucg.ac.me/index.php?page=StudijskiProgramPrikaz&amp;studijski_program=2" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Matematika i raèunarske nauke</a>,&nbsp;<br>akademski studijski program&nbsp;<a href="http://www.pmf.ucg.ac.me/index.php?page=StudijskiProgramPrikaz&amp;studijski_program=3" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Raèunarske nauke</a>,&nbsp;<br>akademski studijski program&nbsp;<a href="http://www.pmf.ucg.ac.me/index.php?page=StudijskiProgramPrikaz&amp;studijski_program=11" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Fizika</a>,&nbsp;<br>akademski studijski program&nbsp;<a href="http://www.pmf.ucg.ac.me/index.php?page=StudijskiProgramPrikaz&amp;studijski_program=9" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Biologija</a><br>primijenjeni studijski program&nbsp;<a href="http://www.pmf.ucg.ac.me/index.php?page=StudijskiProgramPrikaz&amp;studijski_program=4" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Raèunarstvo i informacione tehnologije</a>.&nbsp;<br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px;"><br><a class="title" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Postdiplomske studije.</a>&nbsp;U okviru postdiplomskih studija organizuju se sledeæi specijalistièki i magistarski studijski programi:&nbsp;<br>akademski studijski program&nbsp;<a href="http://www.pmf.ucg.ac.me/index.php?page=StudijskiProgramPrikaz&amp;studijski_program=5" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Matematika</a>&nbsp;(sa šest modula - usmjerenja),<br>akademski studijski program&nbsp;<a href="http://www.pmf.ucg.ac.me/index.php?page=StudijskiProgramPrikaz&amp;studijski_program=7" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Raèunarske nauke</a>,&nbsp;<br>akademski studijski program&nbsp;<a href="http://www.pmf.ucg.ac.me/index.php?page=StudijskiProgramPrikaz&amp;studijski_program=12" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Fizika</a>,&nbsp;<br>akademski studijski program&nbsp;<a href="http://www.pmf.ucg.ac.me/index.php?page=StudijskiProgramPrikaz&amp;studijski_program=10" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Biologija.</a></p><br><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px;"></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px;"><a class="title" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Doktorske studije.</a>&nbsp;Na Prirodno-matematièkom fakultetu u okviru doktorskih studija organizuju se:&nbsp;<br>studijski program&nbsp;<a href="http://www.pmf.ucg.ac.me/index.php?page=StudijskiProgramPrikaz&amp;studijski_program=13" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Matematika</a>,&nbsp;<br>studijski program&nbsp;<a href="http://www.pmf.ucg.ac.me/index.php?page=StudijskiProgramPrikaz&amp;studijski_program=15" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Raèunarske nauke</a>,<br>studijski program&nbsp;<a href="http://www.pmf.ucg.ac.me/index.php?page=StudijskiProgramPrikaz&amp;studijski_program=18" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Fizika</a>,<br>studijski program&nbsp;<a href="http://www.pmf.ucg.ac.me/index.php?page=StudijskiProgramPrikaz&amp;studijski_program=17" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Biologija.</a></p><br><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px;"></p></div><h2 id="saradnja" style="margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Nauèno-istraživaèki rad i saradnja sa drugim institucijama</h2><br style="color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">Na fakultetu postoji razvijena nauèno-istraživaèka aktivnost, koja se realizuje kroz projekte Sektora za nauku Ministarstva za obrazovanje Crne Gore, meðunarodne nauène projekte i individualnu djelatnost. Nastavnici i saradnici fakulteta autori su znaèajnog broja radova u prestižnim meðunarodnim nauènim èasopisima.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">Nastavnici i saradnici sa PMF-a su boravili (i borave) na mnogim univerzitetima Rusije, SAD, Velike Britanije, Francuske, Njemaèke, Italije, Švajcarske, Poljske, Belgije, Èehoslovaèke, Japana, Rumunije. Na njima su držali predavanja i bavili se naèno-istraživaèkim radom. Posebno je razvijena saradnja sa Moskovskim državnim univerzitetom "M. V. Lomonosov", na kome su nastavnici i saradnici ovog fakulteta proveli više od 150 godina. Intenzivna je i saradnja sa Ujedinjenim institutom za nuklearno istraživanje u Dubni i Ruskim nauènim centrom "Kurèatovski institut" u Moskvi, a fakultet je uèesnik poznatih kolaboracija u oblasti fizike DESY i HERA-B.</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">Višegodišnja plodna aktivnost nastavnika i saradnika iz oblasti matematike i raèunarskih nauka u oblasti nastavno-obrazovnog i nauèno-istraživèkog rada, rezultirala je nastankom èasopisa Matematika Crne Gore "Mathematica Montisnigri".</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">Èasopis objavljuje originalne nauène radove iz svih oblasti matematike koji sadrže nove i znaèajne rezultate od interesa za veæi broj matematièara u svijetu, kao i radove preglednog karaktera. Radovi prispjeli u èasopis se recenziraju i štampaju na engleskom, ruskom, francuskom i njemaèkom jeziku. Èasopis se razmjenjuje sa preko 80 nauènih èasopisa širom svijeta. Meðu njima su i najpoznatiji nauèni èasopisi matematike SAD, Rusije, Japana,...</p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;">Znaèaj broj diplomiranih matemtièara, fizièara i biologa PMF-a postali su afirmisani nauèni radnici u raznim oblastima. Meðu njima je velik broj onih koji su doktorske disertacije odbranili na poznatim univerzitetima Evrope, SAD i Rusije.</p>', 'da', 'About faculty', 'Version from site (Prevedeno sa google.translate)', '', '<div>faculty development</div><div><br></div><div>Socially commitment to the formation of a higher educational and scientific organization in the field of mathematical and physical sciences , but was officially constituted in 1970. , When the Assembly of the Republic of Montenegro adopted the Program of development of higher education institutions in Montenegro for the period 1971-1975 . year. The concept of such an institution had not yet been fully defined , so that the program mentioned two names : Institute of Mathematics and its Applications and Mathematical Faculty of Physics . Already in Development Program of the University " Veljko Vlahovic " for the period 1976-1980 . The more closely define its physiognomy , because it speaks of the need for the establishment of the Institute of Natural Sciences , a joint educational and scientific units within the University .</div><div>Along with the development of the Technical University of Titograd snažilo ''s staff and its Department of Mathematics and Physics , so the transformation of the Faculty of Engineering , which received social verification on July 14 in 1978. , The constituted Institute of Mathematics and Physics , as a first step in the implementation of the Program development of the University .</div><div>Decision of 7 April in 1980. Was given approval to the curriculum of the Department of Mathematics and Department of Physics . First-generation students in these departments were entered school 1980/81 . year.</div><div>On the 17th of March 1988. Was the Decision approving the renaming of the Institute of Mathematics and Physics, Faculty of Science ( PMF) and the transformation of the Department of Mathematics and Computer Science .</div><div>An important step in the development of the Faculty of Science is the creation of the Department of Biology . First-generation students in this department enrolled in the school year 1991/92 . year.</div><div>2001/02 as part of the Department of Mathematics and Computer Science was established program of study Computer Science , and the following year and applied study program College (later High) School of Computing and Information Technology .</div><div>From the 2004 / 2005th teaching at the university is organized on the principle of a single European educational system , in accordance with the Bologna Declaration . School 2007a. Was performed as a fundamental reorganization of study programs at the Faculty of Science .</div><div>Within the Faculty of Science was ten years ago, as a separate organization unit , radio University Computer Center ( URC) . Task URC has been servicing the teaching and research work at the University of Montenegro in the field of computer science . Now at the Faculty of Science in Computer Centre there PMF as a separate organizational unit . Task Computing Center has been servicing the teaching and research work at the Faculty of computer science and providing services to third parties .</div><div>The organization of teaching</div><div>In college classes are organized on three levels: basic , specialist and master''s graduate and doctoral studies .</div><div><br></div><div>Undergraduate Studies . Within the undergraduate organized five academic and applied a program of study :</div><div>Academic study programs Mathematics</div><div>Academic study program Mathematics and Computer Science ,</div><div>Academic study program Computer Science ,</div><div>academic study program in physics,</div><div>academic program of study Biology</div><div>applied study program Computer Science and Information Technology .</div><div><br></div><div>Postgraduate studies . As part of post-graduate studies are organized following the specialist ''s and master''s degree programs :</div><div>Academic study programs Mathematics ( with six modules - direction )</div><div>Academic study program Computer Science ,</div><div>academic study program in physics,</div><div>academic program of study Biology .</div><div><br></div><div>Doctoral studies . At the Faculty of Sciences in the framework of doctoral studies are organized :</div><div>study Mathematics ,</div><div>study program Computer Science ,</div><div>program of study of physics,</div><div>Biology study program .</div><div><br></div><div>Scientific research and collaboration with other institutions</div><div><br></div><div>The Faculty developed scientific research activities , implemented through projects the Department of Science of the Ministry of Education of Montenegro , the international scientific projects and individual activities . Teachers and Faculty associates authors are a significant number of papers in prestigious international scientific journals .</div><div>Teachers and associates with Science are staying ( and staying ) in many universities of Russia , the U.S. , Britain , France, Germany , Italy, Switzerland , Poland, Belgium , Czechoslovakia , Japan, Romania . On them were lectured and practiced the lar research. Specially developed cooperation with Moscow State University " MV Lomonosov " , in which the teachers and staff of the college spent more than 150 years . Intense and cooperation with the United Institute of Nuclear Research in Dubna and the Russian Scientific Center " Kurèatovski Institute " in Moscow , a faculty participant famous collaboration in the field of physics DESY and HERA -B .</div><div>Many years of fruitful activity of teachers and staff in the field of mathematics and computer science in the field of teaching and education and scientific istraživèkog work resulted in the creation of the journal Mathematics of Montenegro " Mathematica Montisnigri " .</div><div>The journal publishes original research papers in all areas of mathematics which include a new and significant results of interest for a number of mathematicians in the world , as well as review papers character . Compositions in the journal are peer-reviewed and published in English , Russian, French and German. The magazine is exchanged with over 80 scientific journals around the world . Among them are the best-known scientific journals of mathematics United States , Russia, Japan , ...</div><div>The significance of the number of graduates matemtièara , physicists and biologists Science became renowned scholars in various fields. Among them are many who are doctoral thesis defended at famous universities in Europe, USA and Russia.</div>'),
