(1, 'ne', 'menusaradnja', 'Saradnja', 'Verzija sa sajta', '<h2 style="margin-bottom: 5px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Tempus</h2><br style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px;"><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px;">PMF je višegodišnji saradnik na Tempus projektu. Više informacija o ovom meðunarodnog projektu možete dobiti na&nbsp;<a href="http://ec.europa.eu/education/programmes/tempus/index_en.html" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">sajtu.</a></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px;"><i>".....Tempus promotes the voluntary convergence with EU developments in higher education deriving from the Lisbon Strategy to create more jobs and growth, and the Bologna Process to establish a European Area of Higher Education.</i></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px;"><i>Tempus finances&nbsp;<u>two types of action</u>&nbsp;through regular calls for proposals published on this website.</i></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px;"><i>1)&nbsp;<b>Joint Projects</b>&nbsp;are based on multilateral partnerships between higher education institutions in the EU and the partner countries. They can develop, modernise and disseminate new curricula, teaching methods or materials, boost a quality assurance culture, and modernise the management and governance of higher education institutions.</i></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px;"><i>2)&nbsp;<b>Structural Measures</b>&nbsp;contribute to the development and reform of higher education institutions and systems in partner countries, to enhance their quality and relevance, and increase their convergence with EU developments.</i></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 5px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px;"><i>The European Commission has launched a complementary higher education cooperation programme with countries surrounding the European Union: the&nbsp;<a target="_blank" href="http://eacea.cec.eu.int/static/en/mundus/extcoop/call/index.htm" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: inherit; cursor: pointer; background-position: inherit inherit; background-repeat: inherit inherit;">Erasmus Mundus “External Co-operation Window”</a>. It funds higher education student and teaching staff mobility activities between European universities and universities from targeted third-countries....."<br></i></p><br style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px;"><br style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Programe postdiplomskih studija na svim studijskim programima možete preuzeti u pdf formatu sa ovog</span><a href="http://www.pmf.ucg.ac.me/skladiste/staticke/TEMPUS_PMF_2007.pdf" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); cursor: pointer; font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px;">linka</a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">. Detalje o tempus projektu u Crnoj Gori možete dobiti&nbsp;</span><a target="_blank" href="http://www.tempus.pmf.cg.ac.yu/" style="color: rgb(224, 105, 26); background-image: inherit; background-size: inherit; background-attachment: inherit; background-origin: inherit; background-clip: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); cursor: pointer; font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px;">ovdje</a><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Tahoma, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 16.799999237060547px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">.</span>', 'da', 'Cooperation', 'Version from site (prevedeno sa google.translate)', '', '<div>Tempus</div><div><br></div><div>PMF is a perennial contributor to the Tempus project. More information about this international project is available on the website.</div><div>" ..... Tempus promotes the voluntary convergence with EU developments in higher education deriving from the Lisbon Strategy to create more jobs and growth , and the Bologna Process to establish a European Area of Higher Education .</div><div>Tempus finances two types of action through regular calls for proposals published on this website .</div><div>1 ) Joint Projects are based on multilateral partnerships between higher education institutions in the EU and the partner countries . They can develop, modernize and disseminate new curricula , teaching methods or materials , boost a quality assurance culture , and modernize the management and governance of higher education institutions .</div><div>2 ) Structural Measures contribute to the development and reform of higher education institutions and systems in partner countries , to enhance their quality and relevance , and increase their convergence with EU developments .</div><div>The European Commission has launched a complementary Higher Education Cooperation Programme with countries surrounding the European Union : the Erasmus Mundus "External Co -operation Window". It funds higher education student and teaching staff mobility activities between European universities and universities from targeted third- countries ..... "</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>Programs of graduate study in all study programs can be downloaded in pdf format from this link . Details of the Tempus project in Montenegro can be obtained here .</div>'),
